11 septembre 2001 : l'effroyable imposture idiots , mesonges it is puzzling why so many of the french have been willing to pay the equivalent of $ 17 for `` the horrifying fraud . '' is it a symptom of latent anti-americanism ? is it a reflection of the french public 's famous distrust of its own government and mainstream newspapers ? or has the french love of logic been tickled by the apparent cartesian neatness of a conspiracy theory ?